methods.of:
Optimizes a collection of aggregations by grouping like-specced aggregations together. The
 input order will be preserved based on the spec-encountered order.

:param aggregations: (java.util.Collection<? extendsio.deephaven.api.agg.Aggregation>) - the aggregations
:return: (java.util.List<io.deephaven.api.agg.Aggregation>) the optimized aggregations
